                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">WinFaceTracke nos ha ayudado a reducir el tiempo de gestión en un 50%.</p>
                        </div>
                        <footer class="mt-4">
                            <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Empresa XYZ</p>
                        </footer>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Testimonio 2 -->
                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
                    <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-gray-400 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                                <path d="M9.352 4C4.456 7.456 1 13.12 1 19.36c0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.36 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.208-5.472-5.088-5.472-.576 0-1.344.096-1.536.192.48-3.264 3.552-7.104 6.624-9.024L9.352 4zm16.512 0c-4.8 3.456-8.256 9.12-8.256 15.36 0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.264 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.304-5.472-5.184-5.472-.576 0-1.248.096-1.44.192.48-3.264 3.456-7.104 6.528-9.024L25.864 4z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">La mejor herramienta para mantener la información de empleados organizada.</p>
                        </div>
                        <footer class="mt-4">
                            <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Juan Pérez</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Gerente de Recursos Humanos</p>
                        </footer>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Testimonio 3 -->
                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
                    <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-gray-400 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                                <path d="M9.352 4C4.456 7.456 1 13.12 1 19.36c0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.36 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.208-5.472-5.088-5.472-.576 0-1.344.096-1.536.192.48-3.264 3.552-7.104 6.624-9.024L9.352 4zm16.512 0c-4.8 3.456-8.256 9.12-8.256 15.36 0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.264 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.304-5.472-5.184-5.472-.576 0-1.248.096-1.44.192.48-3.264 3.456-7.104 6.528-9.024L25.864 4z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Gracias a WinFaceTracke, podemos tomar decisiones basadas en datos precisos.</p>
                        </div>
                        <footer class="mt-4">
                            <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Ana Gómez</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Directora de Operaciones</p>
                        </footer>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sección de Contacto -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl mb-4">
                ¿Necesitas Ayuda?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
                Estamos aquí para ayudarte. Si tienes alguna pregunta, no dudes en contactarnos.
            </p>
            <a href="/Contacto" 
               class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105">
                Contáctanos
                <svg class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Moderno -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-900">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Enlaces Rápidos -->
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Enlaces Rápidos</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li>
                            <a href="/Empleados" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">
                                Empleados
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="/Asistencia" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">
                                Asistencia
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="/Reportes" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">
                                Reportes
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Redes Sociales -->
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Síguenos</h3>
                    <div class="flex space-x-4">
                        <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200">
